/*

    Does a Mindblast against the selected Target

    Range    : 15.0f,
    DC       : 10+ casterlevel/2 + wisdome modifier
    Duration : d4()

*/
//:://////////////////////////////////////////////
//:: Created By: Georg Zoeller
//:: Created On: July, 07, 2003
